&lt;li&gt;Juliana Maria Oliveira dos Santos - Universidade Federal da Bahia&lt;span class="toggle"&gt;&lt;img src="http://papers.softwarelivre.org/papers_ng/media/img/expand.png" align="absmiddle" alt="" style="vertical-align: middle;"&gt;mini-currículo&lt;/span&gt;
